Package: tidywrangle
Type: Package
Title: Load datasets , clean column names and perform checks in a tidy manner
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person('Niraj', 'Juneja', email = 'shambhuone12@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: Utilities for loading datasets and conducting data prep at initial load so that you cna work with the dataset ina tidy manner. Does the following based on a dictionary.Renames columnds to tidy columns.
            drops unsed colums , changes data types , perform basic Data quality checks. etc.
